{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_040.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1d,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's Marion.<CR>Hello... Huh!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's wrong, Marion!?<CR>You're staggering!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xe9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...I haven't been eating well lately..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "That's not good. You should eat every meal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xec,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I am eating. Well, I've been eating<CR>food-like substances..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "F-Food-like substances...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xea,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Linca learned how to cook recently,<CR>so she's been cooking various things<CR>for me, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, how is it going? I taught her how to cook, since she asked me to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xee,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh, so it was you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xf0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Well, for breakfast today, she served me something that resembled eggs."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xf0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It might be better to say it was<CR>a heap of dark brown something.<CR>Dark brown...? Or dark black...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xf2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's a complete mystery to me how<CR>anyone could prepare a dish and<CR>have it end up like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, umm, I also taught her how to grill meat and make stew..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xed,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "She's not skilled enough to cook different things at once."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "So yesterday we had a large quantity of stew for lunch, and a large quantity of grilled meat for dinner."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I think I remember hearing her say that making a large quantity will make it taste better."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's... I-I'm sorry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why are you apologizing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Well, umm, about large quantities making it taste good..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I guess I didn't quite get the right idea across..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry I wasn't able to teach her how to cook better."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It's fine. I was worried that Linca might've been causing problems for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I think you can kinda tell already, but she's completely helpless when it comes to anything other than her sword."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I want her to be happy about normal stuff, now that she's met you and all, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I guess that won't happen for a while..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Ah, well, I'll get going now.<CR>Thanks, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Oh, and I wonder why she always puts a flag on her dishes now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I heard her say something like,<CR>\"I raised another flag today...\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "(I kinda feel responsible.<CR>If I taught her better...)"
        }
    ]
}